T1  - A knowledge-based view of managing dependence on a key customer: Survival and growth outcomes for young firms
AU  - Yli-Renko, Helena
AU  - Denoo, Lien
AU  - Janakiraman, Ramkumar
JO  - Journal of Business Venturing
VL  - 35
IS  - 6
SP  - 106045
